General.Name: Redcastle Resources Ltd
General.Description: Redcastle Resources Limited, through its subsidiary, a gold and mineral resources exploration company in Australia. It holds a 100% interest in the Redcastle Gold Project that covers an area of 1,088 hectares located in the Mt Margaret Mineral Field of Western Australia. The company was formerly known as Transcendence Technologies Limited and changed its name to Redcastle Resources Limited in December 2021. Redcastle Resources Limited was incorporated in 2001 and is based in Subiaco, Australia.
